{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"readonly","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgress","text":"MLNOfflinePackProgress","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@MLNOfflinePackProgress","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"progress","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The progress of an inactive or completed pack is computed lazily, and all its","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"fields are set to 0 by default. To request the pack’s progress, use the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-requestProgress"},{"text":" method. To get notified when the progress becomes","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"known and when it changes, observe KVO change notifications on this pack’s","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"state"},{"text":" key path. Alternatively, you can add an observer for","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":"s about this pack that come from the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"default notification center.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack"]]},"sections":[],"metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"progress"}],"role":"symbol","symbolKin